                        2(14)(b)</ref>)</enactingFormula><sourceNote>(Enacting provision omitted—<ref href="hk/2018/er2">E.R. 2 of 2018</ref>)<marker role="blank-line"></marker><marker role="blank-line"></marker></sourceNote><commencementNote>[28 December 2001]</commencementNote><sourceNote>(Format changes—<ref href="hk/2018/er2">E.R. 2 of 2018</ref>)</sourceNote><section id="ID_1438402732898_003" name="s1" reason="inEffect" startPeriod="2018-04-26" status="operational" temporalId="s1"><num value="1">1.</num><heading>Declaration</heading><leadIn>It is declared that a person is not a money broker for the purposes of the
            definition of <b><i>money broker</i></b> by reason only of his negotiating, arranging or
            facilitating, whether by electronic means or otherwise, any or both of the
            following—</leadIn><paragraph id="ID_1438411323830_038" name="a" temporalId="s1_a"><num value="a">(a)</num><content>the syndication of loans under which two or more persons provide credit or lend
                money to one or more other persons; or</content></paragraph><paragraph id="ID_1438411323830_046" name="b" temporalId="s1_b"><num value="b">(b)</num><content>the issue of debt securities.</content></paragraph></section></main></subLeg>